{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":900,"text":"When I turned 19, I started my career"},{"time":3555,"text":"as the first female photojournalist"},{"time":5985,"text":"in the Gaza Strip, Palestine."},{"time":9180,"text":"My work as a woman photographer"},{"time":11294,"text":"was considered a serious insult"},{"time":13398,"text":"to local traditions,"},{"time":15153,"text":"and created a lasting stigma"},{"time":17201,"text":"for me and my family."},{"time":20010,"text":"The male-dominated field made my presence"},{"time":23022,"text":"unwelcome by all possible means."},{"time":26092,"text":"They made clear that a woman"},{"time":27810,"text":"must not do a man's job."},{"time":30407,"text":"Photo agencies in Gaza refused to train me"},{"time":32747,"text":"because of my gender."},{"time":35210,"text":"The \"No\" sign was pretty clear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37933,"text":"Three of my colleagues"},{"time":39304,"text":"went as far as to drive me to an open air strike area"},{"time":44180,"text":"where the explosion sounds"},{"time":46156,"text":"were the only thing I could hear."},{"time":48451,"text":"Dust was flying in the air,"},{"time":50566,"text":"and the ground was shaking like a swing beneath me."},{"time":54525,"text":"I only realized we weren't\nthere to document the event"},{"time":57878,"text":"when the three of them got back into the armored Jeep"},{"time":60848,"text":"and drove away, waving and laughing,"},{"time":63502,"text":"leaving me behind in the open air strike zone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68351,"text":"For a moment, I felt terrified,"},{"time":71388,"text":"humiliated, and sorry for myself."},{"time":75623,"text":"My colleagues' action was not"},{"time":77687,"text":"the only death threat I have received,"},{"time":80354,"text":"but it was the most dangerous one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":84392,"text":"The perception of women's life in Gaza"},{"time":87407,"text":"is passive."},{"time":89387,"text":"Until a recent time, a lot of \nwomen were not allowed"},{"time":92747,"text":"to work or pursue education."},{"time":95717,"text":"At times of such doubled war including"},{"time":98788,"text":"both social restrictions on women"},{"time":100970,"text":"and the Israeli-Palestinian conflict,"},{"time":103954,"text":"women's dark and bright stories were fading away."},{"time":107972,"text":"To men, women's stories were seen"},{"time":110300,"text":"as inconsequential."}]},{"cues":[{"time":112257,"text":"I started paying closer attention"},{"time":115329,"text":"to women's lives in Gaza."},{"time":117366,"text":"Because of my gender, I had access"},{"time":120065,"text":"to worlds where my colleagues were forbidden."},{"time":124643,"text":"Beyond the obvious pain and struggle,"},{"time":127077,"text":"there was a healthy dose"},{"time":128862,"text":"of laughter and accomplishments."},{"time":131682,"text":"In front of a police compound in Gaza City"},{"time":135201,"text":"during the first war in Gaza,"},{"time":138240,"text":"an Israeli air raid managed to destroy the compound"},{"time":141593,"text":"and break my nose."},{"time":143740,"text":"For a moment, all I saw was white, bright white,"},{"time":148351,"text":"like these lights."},{"time":150848,"text":"I thought to myself I either got blind"},{"time":154211,"text":"or I was in heaven."},{"time":157100,"text":"By the time I managed to open my eyes,"},{"time":160320,"text":"I had documented this moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164531,"text":"Mohammed Khader, a Palestinian worker"},{"time":166874,"text":"who spent two decades in Israel,"},{"time":170043,"text":"as his retirement plan,"},{"time":171936,"text":"he decided to build a four-floor house,"},{"time":175266,"text":"only by the first field operation at his neighborhood,"},{"time":179563,"text":"the house was flattened to the ground."},{"time":182995,"text":"Nothing was left but the pigeons he raised"},{"time":186544,"text":"and a jacuzzi, a bathtub"},{"time":189709,"text":"that he got from Tel Aviv."},{"time":191953,"text":"Mohammed got the bathtub"},{"time":193750,"text":"on the top of the rubble"},{"time":195516,"text":"and started giving his kids"},{"time":198140,"text":"an every morning bubble bath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202198,"text":"My work is not meant to hide the scars of war,"},{"time":205460,"text":"but to show the full frame"},{"time":207541,"text":"of unseen stories of Gazans."},{"time":210748,"text":"As a Palestinian female photographer,"},{"time":214122,"text":"the journey of struggle, survival and everyday life"},{"time":218830,"text":"has inspired me to overcome the community taboo"},{"time":222151,"text":"and see a different side of war and its aftermath."},{"time":227318,"text":"I became a witness with a choice:"},{"time":231390,"text":"to run away or stand still."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235170,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237408,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}